                  <div class="px-4 pb-3 hidden faq-answer">
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                      Yes. qSOFA has limited sensitivity. A score of 0 or 1 does
                      <strong>not</strong> exclude sepsis or the need for
                      treatment. Always consider the overall clinical picture,
                      laboratory results, and other early warning scores or
                      sepsis screening tools used in your institution.
                    </p>
                  </div>
